No. 10-8137 (R46-013). Asuncion Avila-Villa, Petitioner v. Ohio. 562 U.S. 1281, 131 S. Ct. 1630,

179 L. Ed. 2d 521,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 2103. March 17, 2011.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Ohio, Butler County, in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.
